  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong>&nbsp;<em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 119</em></p>\n<p><strong>Aura</strong>&nbsp;moderate transmutation&nbsp;<strong>CL</strong>&nbsp;7th</p>\n<p><strong>Slot</strong>&nbsp;armor/shield quality;&nbsp;<strong>Price</strong>&nbsp;+1 bonus;&nbsp;<strong>Weight</strong>&nbsp;-</p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\"><img style=\"margin: 3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\" src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" /><strong>Description</strong></h3>\n<p>A shield or suit of armor with this special ability is especially hardy. It gains double its enhancement bonus to hardness and hit points (instead of just the enhancement bonus), its break DC increases by double its enhancement bonus, and it gains a bonus on saving throws against direct attacks (such as a rust monster's rust ability) equal to its enhancement bonus.</p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong>&nbsp;Craft Magic Arms and Armor,&nbsp;<em>fabricate</em>,&nbsp;<em>make whole</em>;&nbsp;<strong>Price</strong>&nbsp;+1 bonus</p>",
